{{Infobox journal | title = International Journal of Hydrogen Energy | cover = International Journal of Hydrogen Energy.jpg | discipline = [[Hydrogen fuel|Hydrogen energy]] | editor = T. Nejat Veziroglu | abbreviation = Int. J. Hydrog. Energy | publisher = [[Elsevier]] | country = | frequency = weekly | history = 1976—present | impact = 3.582 | impact-year = 2016 | openaccess = | website = http://www.journals.elsevier.com/international-journal-of-hydrogen-energy/ | link2 = http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/journal/03603199 | link2-name = Online archive | link3 = http://www.iahe.org/journal.asp | link3-name = Journal page at society website | ISSN = 0360-3199 | OCLC = 884093395 | CODEN = IJHEDX | LCCN = 76644490 }} The '''''International Journal of Hydrogen Energy''''' is a [[peer-reviewed]] [[scientific journal]] covering all aspects of [[Hydrogen fuel|hydrogen energy]], including [[hydrogen]] generation and [[hydrogen storage|storage]]. It is published by [[Elsevier]] and is an official journal of the [[International Association for Hydrogen Energy]]. Established in 1976, the journal became monthly in 1982, biweekly in 2008, 36/yr in 2013 and weekly in 2015. The [[editor in chief]] is [[Turhan Nejat Veziroğlu]] ([[University of Miami]]).
